<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #dddddd;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #2e2e2e;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 0;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 4px 4px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777777;
            border-top: 1px solid #dddddd;
        }
        .button {
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .highlight {
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Order Received</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear {{customer_name}},</p>
            <p>We are pleased to inform you that your recent order <span class="highlight">{{invoice_id}}</span> placed on <span class="highlight">{{created_at}}</span> has been received.</p>
            <p>You will receive an email invoice shortly. Once your order has been processed, we will notify you again.</p>
            <p>If you have any questions or need further assistance, please do not hesitate to contact our customer support team at <a href="mailto:sales@adventband.org" target="_blank">sales@adventband.org</a> or <a href="mailto:support@adventband.org">support@adventband.org</a>.</p>
            <p>For quick assistance, you can also contact us on WhatsApp:</p>
            <a href="https://wa.me/254741741381" target="_blank" class="button">Contact Us on WhatsApp</a>
            <p>Thank you for shopping with us!</p>
            <p>Sincerely,<br>Advent Band</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2024 Advent Band. All rights reserved.</p>
            <a href="https://adventband.org" target="_blank">Adventist Heritage Community</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
